            "该战略还包括 Codex 和公司级 AI 代理的开发。"
          ]
        },
        "impact": {
          "en": "This outline from OpenAI indicates a strategic focus on integrating advanced AI solutions into enterprise environments. The acceleration of adoption suggests a shift towards broader practical implementation of AI across diverse sectors.",
          "zh": "OpenAI 的这一阐述表明其战略重点在于将先进 AI 解决方案整合到企业环境中。采纳的加速预示着 AI 在各行各业的实际应用正向更广泛的范围转变。"
        },
        "source": "OpenAI News",
        "link": "https://openai.com/index/next-phase-of-enterprise-ai"
